{
  "stem": "11174.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was an English concession what's called Together with America that they controlled that area.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a French concession-- a whole part of the town that was controlled by the French.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And than was a [INAUDIBLE] which was controlled by the Japanese.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because there was no Chinese government in that area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The capital of the Chinese government that was under Japanese control was Nanking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- the Communists was in the rest of the country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we-- everybody [INAUDIBLE] at least according to the alphabet-- earlier had to go earlier.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was on the list one day, and we went to Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a boat-- a Japanese boat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Joint probably.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we arrived to Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very short time before Yom-- Rosh Hashanah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Started out from-- oh, it's-- is more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is-- this is already summer of '41, this is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Shanghai, I started a new life completely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shanghai there was starting a committee with a restaurant-- with a kitchen for us, which was also supported by the Joint for a while.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not-- then-- then the Japan-- when Japan went in the war-- Japan wasn't in the war yet now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When Germany attacked Russia the 22nd of June, Japan was still not in the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They sent us away because they knew they were gonna get in the war, apparently.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in Shanghai we were for a while, and it was still American representative there, English, and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden, when Japan attacked Pearl Harbor, it was a new story completely.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They started to have control on us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they started-- they put us after a while-- they put us into a restricted area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You had to have a sort of a passport.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
